News.headline: Fixture News: The Emirates FA Cup – 4th Qualifying Round
News.page_title: Fixture News: The Emirates FA Cup – 4th Qualifying Round
News.URL_keywords: Fixture News: The Emirates FA Cup – 4th Qualifying Round
News.short_description: Dagenham & Redbridge have been drawn to play Wealdstone FC at home in the 4th qualifying round of the Emirates FA Cup.
News.description:
The game will be played on Saturday 15th October.

Details for the game will be announced in due course.
